</ul>
<p><a name="Examples" id="Examples"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=False_flag&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: Examples">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Examples</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Canuck_Letter" title="Canuck Letter">Canuck Letter</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Gleiwitz_incident" title="Gleiwitz incident">Gleiwitz incident</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Bloed,_Bodem,_Eer_en_Trouw" title="Bloed, Bodem, Eer en Trouw">Bloed, Bodem, Eer en Trouw</a></i> (Flemish neo-Nazi group preparing false flag attacks)</li>
<li>February 27, 1933 <a href="/wiki/Reichstag_Fire" title="Reichstag Fire" class="mw-redirect">Reichstag Fire</a>, which led to the <a href="/wiki/Reichstag_Fire_Decree" title="Reichstag Fire Decree">Reichstag Fire Decree</a> which suspended the <a href="/wiki/Weimar_Constitution" title="Weimar Constitution">Weimar Constitution</a> until the end of the <a href="/wiki/Third_Reich" title="Third Reich" class="mw-redirect">Third Reich</a></li>
<li>TPAJAX, <a href="/wiki/CIA" title="CIA" class="mw-redirect">CIA</a> <a href="/wiki/Operation_Ajax" title="Operation Ajax" class="mw-redirect">Operation Ajax</a> (<a href="/wiki/USA" title="USA" class="mw-redirect">USA</a> overthrowing of Mohammed Mossadeq, Prime Minister of Iran, in 1953)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/SIS" title="SIS">SIS</a> (<a href="/wiki/MI6" title="MI6" class="mw-redirect">MI6</a>) <a href="/wiki/Operation_Boot" title="Operation Boot" class="mw-redirect">Operation Boot</a> (<a href="/wiki/UK" title="UK" class="mw-redirect">UK</a> Operation for overthrowing of Mohammed Mossadeq, Prime Minister of Iran, in 1953 with Americans) <a href="http://www.garretwilson.com/books/reviews/alltheshahsmen.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.garretwilson.com/books/reviews/alltheshahsmen.html" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Operation_Northwoods" title="Operation Northwoods">Operation Northwoods</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Black_Operation" title="Black Operation">Black Operation</a>, Rogue Operation <a href="/w/index.php?title=Project_Cherry&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Project Cherry (page does not exist)">Project Cherry</a> <a href="/wiki/CIA" title="CIA" class="mw-redirect">CIA</a>'s Non-Stop assassination program to kill Prince of <a href="/wiki/Cambodia" title="Cambodia">Cambodia</a> <a href="/wiki/Norodom_Sihanouk" title="Norodom Sihanouk">Norodom Sihanouk</a> <a href="http://johnmccarthy90066.tripod.com/id34.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://johnmccarthy90066.tripod.com/id34.html" rel="nofollow">[2]</a>.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special_Activities_Division" title="Special Activities Division">Special Activities Division</a></li>
<li>The <a href="/wiki/History_of_the_Philippines_(1965-1986)" title="History of the Philippines (1965-1986)" class="mw-redirect">Plaza Miranda Bombings</a> in the <a href="/wiki/Philippines" title="Philippines">Philippines</a>, which led to <a href="/wiki/Ferdinand_Marcos" title="Ferdinand Marcos">Ferdinand Marcos</a>'s suspension of the writ of <a href="/wiki/Habeas_corpus" title="Habeas corpus">habeas corpus</a>.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Shelling_of_Mainila" title="Shelling of Mainila">Shelling of Mainila</a> and <a href="/wiki/Winter_War" title="Winter War">Winter War</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Marxist-Leninist_Party_of_the_Netherlands" title="Marxist-Leninist Party of the Netherlands">Marxist-Leninist Party of the Netherlands</a> (fake party set up by the Dutch security service)</li>
</ul>
